content.text:
Let me analyze both structures in the main target image from left to right:

Structure 1 (Left):
- Has 3 main layers
- Bottom: Red block with circular hole (block #2), with yellow horizontal bars (block #7, #8) above and below
- Middle: Green vertical blocks (block #5, #6) with a yellow horizontal bar (block #7) on top
- Top: Orange triangular piece (block #14 or #15)

Structure 2 (Right):
- Has a base green block (block #4)
- Orange cylindrical column (block #10)
- Frame made of green vertical blocks (block #5, #6)
- Yellow horizontal bars (block #7, #8)
- Green horizontal block on middle layer (block #4)
- Blue cube on top (block #3)
- Orange triangular piece (block #14 or #15) in the middle section

Assembly instructions for both structures:

Left Structure:
{
Step1: Move block with index 7
Step2: Move block with index 2
Step3: Move block with index 8
Step4: Move block with index 5
Step5: Move block with index 6
Step6: Move block with index 7
Step7: Move block with index 14
}

Right Structure:
{
Step1: Move block with index 4
Step2: Move block with index 10
Step3: Move block with index 5
Step4: Move block with index 6
Step5: Move block with index 7
Step6: Move block with index 8
Step7: Move block with index 4
Step8: Move block with index 15
Step9: Move block with index 3
}
